{"tid":676247,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子潛入長安邨單位被制服　揭發為特遣隊警員","createTime":"2018-05-24T08:21:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T09:01:18.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ee004430fb27edc91825ba8b021d9696224adfea","tid":676247,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T08:21:22.000Z","msg":"【15:30】疑犯被黑布蒙頭，雙手反鎖扣上手銬，被警員押返現場調查，逗留約半小時再被帶返警署扣查，而現場探員未有就案情透露半句<br />\n<br />\n【13:45】消息指，涉案男子為一名特遣隊警員，為該大廈住客，暫時未知他於案發時是否正在當值，重案組探員正調查他現身單位的原因<br />\n<br />\n【10:25】葵青警區重案組接手調查<br />\n<br />\n早上7時半，青衣長安邨安湄樓發生爆竊案。男女住戶外出後因事折返，不料大門虛掩，赫見一名陌生男子大模廝樣坐在客廳，懷疑他潛入爆竊，連忙將他截住及報警。警方在疑犯身上沒有搜到可疑物品或屬於屋主的物件，調查後戶主並無損失，列企圖爆竊案處理，疑犯事後被警方拘捕帶走調查。"},{"pid":"a8ee24cdb4d6e8dad7d19e24a0750cb75826f02e","tid":676247,"uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T08:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180524/large/1527148032_6eb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180524%2Flarge%2F1527148032_6eb9.jpg&h=8fc91105&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f191ac072156fda0bbf3e3f232bd1da972a409a","tid":676247,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T08:21:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180524/58230510\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F58230510&d=l%2Bs1Dl%2BLTlmF99EQBzEaT%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=b21a1de7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F58230510&h=32e22b8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180524/58230510</a>"},{"pid":"4588222df3bebca4ee7cae2d697032b872f3ceaf","tid":676247,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T08:26:18.000Z","msg":